item.description: What can the CloudFront do as a CDN? # In reality, CloudFront is a highly versatile Content Delivery Network (CDN) service that can distribute both static and dynamic content. Here are some key points to clarify its capabilities: Multiple Origin Sources: CloudFront can deliver content from various sources, not just S3 buckets. These sources include Amazon EC2 instances, Elastic Load Balancers, and, notably, Amazon API Gateway. Dynamic Content Delivery:
